PrecisAuthorization for the trip to PARIS made by Mrs. JEAN M. AUGUSTINE, M.P. (Etobicoke -- Lakeshore), and Senator Rose-Marie Losier-Cool, from September 21 to September 24, 1997, in order to participate, together with experts and parliamentarians from the francophone community, in a symposium on population issues.
